divergence_from_c:
Return type: C `int` -> TS `number`. Numeric value identical. The enum constants are not redefined in the TS port -- the port computes the value inline:

  switch (x.kind) {
    case 'nan':    return 0;
    case 'inf':    return 1 * x.sign;
    case 'zero':   return 2 * x.sign;
    case 'normal': return 3 * x.sign;
  }

Validates against the locked MPFR shape from src/core.ts.
